people.org/dream/50-smooth-sayings-or-surrender/" itemprop="url">50. Smooth Sayings Or Surrender</a></li>\n<li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-dream menu-item-492"><a href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/51-come-aside-and-unify/" itemprop="url">51. Come Aside and Unify</a></li>\n<li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-dream menu-item-17852"><a href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/52-justice-and-mercy/" itemprop="url">52. Justice and Mercy</a></li>\n<li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-dream menu-item-494"><a href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/53-where-are-you-looking/" itemprop="url">53. Where Are You Looking?</a></li>\n<li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-dream menu-item-495"><a href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/54-the-journey-home/" itemprop="url">54. The Journey Home</a></li>\n</ul></div><div class="clear"></div>\n\t\t\t<style>\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2 {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2 ul.wpsm-arrow-enabled:before {  } \n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2 ul, #short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2 ul ul {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2 a {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2 a:hover {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2 ul a {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2 ul a:hover {  }\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</style>\n\t\t\t<script type="text/javascript">\n\t\t\t\tvar show_arrow = "true";var $sm = jQuery.noConflict();\n\t\t\t\t\tjQuery(function ($) {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$("#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2").tinyNav();\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$("#short_menu_5b8b174bedfd2").next().addClass("shortcode-menu-mobile");\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tshortcode_menu_responsive();\n\t\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t\t\tjQuery(window).resize(function($){\n\t\t\t\t\t\tshortcode_menu_responsive();\n\t\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t\t\tfunction shortcode_menu_responsive()\n\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tvar window_width = $sm(window).width();\n\t\t\t\t\t\tif(window_width <= 650)\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t$sm("#short_